source.name: Data.gov Datasets Download By Data Category
source.description: This dataset provides downloads for different data categories in Data.gov. Download represents the number of times a user has clicked on the "XML" or "CSV" (for example) links in the Raw Data Catalogs to download datasets and user downloads of tools in the Tool Catalog available in these categories.
